  Outline
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
The father of Wong Fei-hong, who has been attempting to teach his son kung-fu,
but has found him too disobedient to teach and decides to send him off to his 
uncle, a cruel and torturous master of the 8-Drunken Genii kung-fu. After much 
suffering the son comes back to rescue the father from an assassin who has also 
previously humiliated Naughty Panther. 
A great showcase of Jackie Chan's slapstick comedic talents.
